title: Kaceytron was right.
body:
She said the reason she moved from WoW to League is because the WoW community already knows their game is a joke, but the League community thinks too much of their game.. I didnt understand what she meant by that first

until I came by this cringe worthy video  

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nxAabW7JfTQ

I actually cant listen to that without feeling embarrassed from myself because im actually hearing this.
